    <item>
      <title>摇摆州法院因选举前投票规则爆发争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/election-lawsuits-flare-over-swing-state-voting-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缺席投票和提前投票即将开始，法官们正在竞相解决许多发生在摇摆州的争端，争端涉及美国人在 11 月 5 日的总统选举中如何投票和计票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/election-lawsuits-flare-over-swing-state-voting-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院议长约翰逊称共和党大获全胜将使拜登的气候法遭遇失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/speaker-johnson-says-gop-sweep-would-doom-biden-s-climate-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普赢得总统大选，并且共和党在 11 月大选后确保国会的控制权，那么总统乔·拜登签署的气候法将成为共和党的早期目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/speaker-johnson-says-gop-sweep-would-doom-biden-s-climate-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:24:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多摆脱蒙特利尔失利阴影 但工党面临选举惨败风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trudeau-shakes-off-montreal-loss-but-party-faces-risk-of-election-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自由党在蒙特利尔失去一个关键席位后，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多依然态度坚定，敦促选民更认真地考虑下次选举中将面临的政治选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trudeau-shakes-off-montreal-loss-but-party-faces-risk-of-election-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟首任国防事务专员为工业发行联合债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-s-first-defense-commissioner-floats-joint-bonds-for-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟首任国防部长安德鲁斯·库比柳斯 (Andrius Kubilius) 表示，值得探讨发行联合债券的选择，以筹集推动欧盟工业发展所需的额外 5000 亿欧元（5560 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/eu-s-first-defense-commissioner-floats-joint-bonds-for-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 17:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称巴西的紧缩周期将低于市场预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-s-tightening-cycle-set-to-miss-market-forecast-jpm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通拉美经济研究主管表示，由于美联储的宽松周期为风险资产提供了“金发姑娘”情景，巴西加息幅度将低于交易员的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-s-tightening-cycle-set-to-miss-market-forecast-jpm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 17:25:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马丛林移民至美国人数因管制收紧减少 80%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/tighter-curbs-cut-migration-to-us-through-panama-s-jungle-by-80</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统乔·拜登和巴拿马新政府实施更加严格的管控后，通过危险的达连丛林路线前往美国的移民数量降至两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/tighter-curbs-cut-migration-to-us-through-panama-s-jungle-by-80</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 17:25:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西将加强在线博彩监管以应对赌博“流行病”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-to-bolster-online-betting-rules-amid-gambling-epidemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心家庭为了投注体育和其他游戏而花光积蓄并背上债务，巴西将收紧在线赌博法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/brazil-to-bolster-online-betting-rules-amid-gambling-epidemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:58:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙首席执行官抨击拜登暂停液化天然气出口，称其成本高、排放高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/chevron-ceo-wirth-attacks-biden-lng-export-pause-on-costs-emissions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司首席执行官迈克·沃斯呼吁拜登政府撤销暂停发放液化天然气新出口许可证的决定，称该政策是“重政治轻进步”的失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/chevron-ceo-wirth-attacks-biden-lng-export-pause-on-costs-emissions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 SPAC 创始人赢得运营 Truth Social 公司的 800,000 多股股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-spac-founder-orlando-wins-more-shares-in-media-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在联邦监管机构指控他误导投资者两个月后，特拉华州一家法院判定将唐纳德·特朗普社交媒体公司上市的公司前负责人获得了约 80 万股特朗普媒体科技集团公司的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/trump-spac-founder-orlando-wins-more-shares-in-media-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党称以色列策划黎巴嫩境内传呼机爆炸事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的真主党指责以色列策划了这次袭击，造成黎巴嫩境内数人死亡，近 3,000 人受伤，这加剧了人们对爆发全面战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/pagers-in-lebanon-blast-including-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
